<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Seifrid von Gosheim</head><p>Der Rat teilt erneut mit, dass er mit Gilbrecht von Büches ausgerichtet ist, und bittet um Freundschaft.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_141" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_141_r2l10"><expan>Seıfrıd<ex>en</ex></expan> von Goſheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_141_r2l11"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Seıfrıd als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch niht dunk / daʒ wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l12">an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒwein brıefen . den vollen nach <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> brıefs <expan>auſweıſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l13"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch ın <expan>bede<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l14"><expan>brıefe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> daʒ wır mıt <expan>Geılbrecht<ex>en</ex></expan> von püchıs vnd mıt <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l16">dıe <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_141_r2l15">gewant </ab></add> geweſt ſınt . gütlıch berıcht ſein . vnd ewch auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l17">keins <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan> gewartt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Vnd daʒ wır ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l18">ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> denn guts vnd eẅch <expan>deſgleıch<ex>en</ex></expan> auch getrawen / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l19">dunkt vns daʒ wır eẅch da mit den vollen <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l20"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd getrawen wır eẅch . daʒ Jr <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt vns noch den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l21">niht args ʒu <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> habt das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_141_r2l22"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_141" id="70v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Seifrid<ex>en</ex></expan> von Gosheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Seifrid, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch niht dunk, daz
                        wir ewch an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zwein briefen den vollen nach
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> briefs
                            <expan>ausweisu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch in <expan>bede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>briefe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben,</ex></expan> daz wir mit
                                <expan>Geilbrecht<ex>en</ex></expan> von Püchis und mit
                                <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den, die
                            <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dacht</expan> und <add>gewant</add> gewest sint, gütlich
                        bericht sein und ewch auch keins <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan> gewartt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und daz wir zu
                            <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> denn guts und ewch
                            <expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> auch getrawen. Und dunkt uns, daz
                        wir ewch da mit den vollen <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> haben.
                                <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> und getrawen wir ewch, daz ir
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> mit uns noch den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht args zu
                            <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> habt; das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Judica. </ab>
</div>
